		{"id":"quantum_computing","type":"text","text":"# 💠 量子计算\n\n**量子优越性**\n$$|\\psi\\rangle = \\alpha|0\\rangle + \\beta|1\\rangle$$\n\n**Shor算法**\n多项式时间因数分解\n\n**量子纠错**\n$$|L\\rangle = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}(|000\\rangle + |111\\rangle)$$","x":2700,"y":1000,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"information_theory","type":"text","text":"# 📡 信息论\n\n**香农熵**\n$$H(X) = -\\sum_{i} p_i \\log p_i$$\n\n**信道容量**\n$$C = \\max_{p(x)} I(X;Y)$$\n\n**压缩极限**\n熵是信息的本质度量","x":3000,"y":650,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"industrial_rev","type":"text","text":"# ⚙️ 工业革命\n\n**能源转型**\n生物能 → 化石能 → 核能 → ?\n\n**生产力爆发**\n$$GDP = A \\cdot K^\\alpha \\cdot L^{1-\\alpha}$$\n\n技术进步是增长的源泉","x":-500,"y":1700,"width":400,"height":250,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"neural_networks","type":"text","text":"# 🕸️ 神经网络\n\n**深度学习革命**\n\n```python\nclass Transformer:\n    def attention(Q, K, V):\n        scores = Q @ K.T / sqrt(d_k)\n        weights = softmax(scores)\n        return weights @ V\n```\n\n**涌现能力**\n- 上下文学习\n- 思维链推理\n- 代码生成","x":3450,"y":600,"width":400,"height":350,"color":"4"},
