		{"id":"simulation_hypothesis","type":"text","text":"# 🖥️ 模拟假说\n\n**Bostrom论证**\n1. 文明灭绝\n2. 不模拟祖先\n3. 我们在模拟中\n\n**计算资源**\n模拟宇宙需要多少算力？\n\n**递归模拟**\n模拟中的模拟...","x":2550,"y":2100,"width":400,"height":350,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"anthropic_principle","type":"text","text":"# 🎯 人择原理\n\n**微调问题**\n- 精细结构常数: α = 1/137\n- 宇宙学常数: Λ ≈ 10⁻¹²⁰\n\n**多重宇宙**\n无限宇宙中必然存在观察者","x":3000,"y":2200,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"omega_point","type":"text","text":"# Ω 终极奇点\n\n**信息理论极限**\n$$I_{max} = \\frac{kT\\tau}{\\hbar \\ln 2}$$\n\n**计算的物理极限**\n- Landauer原理\n- Margolus-Levitin定理\n- 黑洞计算机\n\n**宇宙的最终命运**\n热寂？大撕裂？循环？","x":3500,"y":2150,"width":450,"height":400,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"great_filter","type":"text","text":"# 🚧 大过滤器\n\n**费米悖论**\n\"他们都在哪里？\"\n\n**可能的过滤器**\n- 生命起源\n- 智能进化\n- 技术爆炸\n- 自我毁灭\n- ？？？\n\n我们是否已经通过？","x":-500,"y":2200,"width":350,"height":300,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"fractal_dimension","type":"text","text":"# 🌿 分形维度\n\n**曼德勃罗集**\n$$z_{n+1} = z_n^2 + c$$\n\n**豪斯多夫维度**\n$$D = \\lim_{\\epsilon \\to 0} \\frac{\\log N(\\epsilon)}{\\log(1/\\epsilon)}$$\n\n- 海岸线: D ≈ 1.25\n- 云朵: D ≈ 2.35\n- 大脑皮层: D ≈ 2.79","x":50,"y":-1700,"width":350,"height":350,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"cellular_automata","type":"text","text":"# 🔲 元胞自动机\n\n**规则110 - 图灵完备**\n\n```javascript\n// Conway生命游戏\nfunction nextGen(grid) {\n  return grid.map((row, i) =>\n    row.map((cell, j) => {\n      const n = countNeighbors(i, j);\n      return (cell && n === 2) || n === 3;\n    })\n  );\n}\n```\n\n简单规则→复杂行为","x":-450,"y":-1650,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"emergence_spiral","type":"text","text":"# 🌀 涌现螺旋\n\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    粒子 --> 原子\n    原子 --> 分子\n    分子 --> 细胞\n    细胞 --> 组织\n    组织 --> 器官\n    器官 --> 生物\n    生物 --> 生态\n    生态 --> 盖亚\n    盖亚 --> ?\n```\n\n每一层都有新的规律","x":800,"y":800,"width":350,"height":450,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"network_science","type":"text","text":"# 🕸️ 复杂网络\n\n**小世界现象**\n六度分隔理论\n\n**无标度网络**\n$$P(k) \\sim k^{-\\gamma}$$\n\n**网络鲁棒性**\n- 随机失效容忍\n- 蓄意攻击脆弱","x":500,"y":-1600,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"philosophy_systems","type":"file","file":"哲学体系演化.md","x":1800,"y":100,"width":400,"height":300},
		{"id":"consciousness_emergence","type":"text","text":"# 🧠 意识涌现\n\n**整合信息理论**\n$$\\Phi = \\min_{\\pi \\in P} D(p||\\prod_{i} p_i^{\\pi})$$\n\n**全局工作空间**\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n    感知 --> 工作空间\n    记忆 --> 工作空间\n    工作空间 --> 意识\n    意识 --> 行动\n```","x":2200,"y":-400,"width":400,"height":350,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"rna_world","type":"text","text":"# 🧬 RNA世界\n\n**自催化集**\n```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    RNA1 -->|催化| RNA2\n    RNA2 -->|催化| RNA3\n    RNA3 -->|催化| RNA1\n```\n\n核酶的双重角色:\n- 信息载体\n- 催化功能","x":1300,"y":-900,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"evolution_algorithm","type":"text","text":"# 🦎 进化算法\n\n```python\ndef evolution(population):\n    while not converged:\n        fitness = evaluate(population)\n        parents = select(population, fitness)\n        offspring = crossover(parents)\n        offspring = mutate(offspring)\n        population = offspring\n    return best(population)\n```\n\n**红皇后假说**\n持续进化才能生存","x":2100,"y":-900,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"symbiosis","type":"text","text":"# 🤝 共生进化\n\n**线粒体内共生**\n真核细胞的诞生\n\n**协同进化**\n- 花与传粉者\n- 肠道微生物组\n- 文化基因共进化","x":2600,"y":-800,"width":350,"height":250,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"genetic_code","type":"text","text":"# 🔤 遗传密码\n\n**密码子简并性**\n64种密码子 → 20种氨基酸\n\n$$H = -\\sum p_i \\log_2 p_i$$\n\n信息熵与进化压力","x":1700,"y":-850,"width":300,"height":200,"color":"4"},
