		{"id":"mathematics_birth","type":"text","text":"# 🔢 数学诞生\n\n**从计数到抽象**\n\n$$\\mathbb{N} \\subset \\mathbb{Z} \\subset \\mathbb{Q} \\subset \\mathbb{R} \\subset \\mathbb{C}$$\n\n**哥德尔编码**\n$$g(s) = \\prod_{i=1}^n p_i^{a_i}$$\n\n形式系统的极限","x":850,"y":200,"width":400,"height":300,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"scientific_method","type":"text","text":"# 🔬 科学方法\n\n```python\nclass ScientificMethod:\n    def process(self):\n        observation = observe()\n        hypothesis = formulate(observation)\n        prediction = deduce(hypothesis)\n        experiment = test(prediction)\n        if validate(experiment):\n            return theory\n        else:\n            return revise(hypothesis)\n```","x":1350,"y":150,"width":400,"height":350,"color":"1"}
